{"tid":3671,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[全智賢李敏鎬] 藍海傳說討論區","createTime":"2016-11-26T08:27:31.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-25T08:57:16.000Z","uid":3517,"like":7,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1750a6f677dfb5e3524dd9a5d750e2d012ad728c","tid":3671,"uid":3517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T08:27:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/26/161739_a7c22dbaa1d8e32a0eeb132f130a18f9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F26%2F161739_a7c22dbaa1d8e32a0eeb132f130a18f9.jpg&h=ea4439fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《藍色海洋的傳說》（韓語：푸른 바다의 전설，英語：Legend Of The Blue Sea）為韓國SBS於2016年11月16日起播出的水木迷你連續劇，由李敏鎬和全智賢擔綱主演，由《來自星星的你》編劇朴智恩作家執筆，由《城市獵人》、《主君的太陽》、《異鄉人醫生》陳赫導演執導，改編自韓國首部野史集《於于野譚》中的人魚故事，峽谷縣令金聃齡將漁夫捕到的人魚重新放回大海。場景來到現代，講述了地球上處於滅絕危機的最後一隻人魚遇到了都市的天才騙子後，在適應陸地生活的過程中發生的一系列故事。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/26/162407_38a81422a7dbfb534a25dcb5678093fe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F26%2F162407_38a81422a7dbfb534a25dcb5678093fe.jpg&h=05787963&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>李敏鎬</strong><br />\n許俊在／金聃齡<br />\n分飾兩角，亙貫古今。一為朝鮮時代兩班貴族縣令金聃齡；一為現代天才騙子許俊在，利用優越的外表及出色的頭腦，化身為檢察官、律師、醫生、企業家等進行各種詐騙。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRC7PVN6TL7eaUSxMK7RKNNqyerwWWofHJjkrfRrvfpQH?filename=TA9O50.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTA9O50.jpg&h=d4b3f2f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>全智賢</strong><br />\n世華 / 沈清<br />\n從朝鮮時代到現代首爾艱難求生的美麗人魚。在陸地會長出腿來，並有靠着接觸人類而消除他們記憶的能力。"},{"pid":"43cb351a897d4001abc0d5e9d6a497ea5b4d6590","tid":3671,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T08:37:16.000Z","msg":"留名先"},{"pid":"9881373602ba503632bf63cabee3063a93e22e3f","tid":3671,"uid":22221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T08:38:14.000Z","msg":"播到第幾集？"},{"pid":"8ebcca9ac2a4fd9afd14fbacc5d43021706912ee","tid":3671,"uid":3517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T08:54:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>播到第幾集？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n第四集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n韓國逢星期三四播"},{"pid":"4c1ae13eb5de29c2bac6978a017bd8ff558f77fb","tid":3671,"uid":3649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T10:16:42.000Z","msg":"全智賢真係好撚屈機，<br />\n演技唔洗講，<br />\n生完仔出返黎完全無老過無殘過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n套嘢雖然偶然有D位覺得有小小老土，<br />\n不過整體黎講好好笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19edba407e14345896553c828eb110bd0eeb2465","tid":3671,"uid":25840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T14:10:35.000Z","msg":"第4集客串果個係咪牽牛"},{"pid":"107c39c495a3a2744c40532c658ece9e3ff45821","tid":3671,"uid":3517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T15:34:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第4集客串果個係咪牽牛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f8862a48a11510a172ed2a4c6ab1ffabd41330c","tid":3671,"uid":3517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T15:37:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>全智賢真係好撚屈機，<br />\n演技唔洗講，<br />\n生完仔出返黎完全無老過無殘過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n套嘢雖然偶然有D位覺得有小小老土，<br />\n不過整體黎講好好笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好鐘意睇佢搞笑果陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f986e6adf98c64bbf5bda4a84aff660a02fe199","tid":3671,"uid":649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T15:38:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>全智賢真係好撚屈機，<br /